Introduction

Kim Gyuri is a South Korean trainee and actress under Pledis Entertainment.

She debuted as an actress in 2018 in tvN's drama "My Mister". She then continued acting for two years, playing in four dramas until 2020.

In 2024, Kim Gyuri was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was sadly eliminated in the final episode. At that time, she was a trainee under WAKEONE.
